         <p class="breadcrumbs">You are here: <a href="/en.html?id=4">Government.no</a> / <a href="/en/dep/ud.html?id=833">Ministry of Foreign Affairs</a> / <a href="/en/dep/ud/selected-topics.html?id=835">Selected topics</a> / <span>Human rights</span>
