                        Trygve Lie Symposium 2010 on Fundamental Freedoms
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Editorial article, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 21.09.2010]</p>
                <p>The third annual Trygve Lie Symposium on Fundamental Freedoms will be chaired by Norwegian Minister of Foreign Affairs Jonas Gahr Støre at the International Peace Institute in New York on 24 September 2010. This year’s symposium will focus on the UN framework for human rights and business: “Protect, Respect and Remedy”.</p>
                
                
