                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 06.09.2010]</p>
                <p>“We extend our condolences to Aleh Byabenin’s loved ones at this difficult time. I would also like to stress that it is important that the circumstances surrounding his death are clarified quickly and thoroughly,” Foreign Minister Jonas Gahr Støre commented.   </p>
                
                
